Description:
You enter an elven mansion and see that it is divided into two wings, plus the upper floor.

In the right wing you hear some strange noises and when you investigate carefully you see a dracomancer who is turning the frozen elves into zombies.

In the left wing you don't seem to see anyone, what you do see is the stylish lute that Gustav asked for.
DescriptionAction: The cold is really intense and you shouldn't stay here for too long.
